      <contents>
        <PRTPAGE P='121' />
        <SECTNO>
          <aref type='CFR-TIC-SECT'>
            § 
            <subref title='7' part='1b' sect='4' psec='' tq='N'>
              1b.4
            </subref>
          </aref>
        </SECTNO>
        <SUBJECT>
          Exclusion of agencies.
        </SUBJECT>
        <P>
          <npcatch lev='1' id='a'>
            <enum src='gpotxt' cln='1'>
              (a)
            </enum>
          </npcatch>
          <text>
             The USDA agencies and agency units listed in paragraph (b) of this
            section conduct programs and activities that have been found to have
            no individual or cumulative effect on the human environment. The
            USDA agencies and agency units listed in paragraph (b) of this
            section are excluded from the requirements of preparing procedures
            to implement NEPA. Actions of USDA agencies and agency units listed
            in paragraph (b) of this section are categorically excluded from the
            preparation of an EA or EIS unless the agency head determines that
            an action may have a significant environmental effect.
          </text>
        </P>
        <P>
